    <h2 class="font-bold text-center text-xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-violet-400 mt-16 mb-8">Blindness</h2>

    <p class="text-lg/loose md:text-xl/loose lg:text-2xl/loose max-w-prose mb-8">Blindness can be defined as sightlessness or loss of vision. However, the tern blindness doesn't always refer to a loss of vision. It may also refer to partial blindness, or when a persons vision is extremely limited.</p>

    <h3 class="text-center text-xl md:text-xl lg:text-3xl text-violet-400 mt-8 mb-8">Causes of Blindness</h3>

    <p class="text-lg/loose md:text-xl/loose lg:text-2xl/loose max-w-prose mb-8">There are several causes of blindness (not limited to):</p>

    <ul class="list-disc text-lg/loose md:text-xl/loose lg:text-2xl/loose max-w-prose mb-8 ml-8">
        <li class="mb-4">Diabetes</li>
        <li class="mb-4">Macular Degeneration</li>
        <li class="mb-4">Glaucoma</li>
        <li class="mb-4">Accidents or injury to the eye</li>
        <li class="mb-4">Stroke</li>
        <li class="mb-4">Retinitis Pigmentosa</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-center text-xl md:text-xl lg:text-3xl text-violet-400 mt-8 mb-8">Legal Definition of Blindness</h3>

    <p class="text-lg/loose md:text-xl/loose lg:text-2xl/loose max-w-prose mb-8">In the US, there is a legal definition of blindness that is used to determine whether someone can receive benefits and participate in certain programs for schooling or vocational training, assistive devices, and tax exemption. This definition isn't intended to provide information about what a person can or can not see. According to this definition, a person is considered legally blind if they have a visual acuity of 20/200 with corrective lenses or if their field of vision is 20 degrees in the eye that has the best vision.</p>
    
    <h3 class="text-center text-xl md:text-xl lg:text-3xl text-violet-400 mt-8 mb-8">Challenges & Solutions for People Who Are Blind</h3>

    <p class="text-lg/loose md:text-xl/loose lg:text-2xl/loose max-w-prose mb-8">Blind people use screen readers to get information from the web. Screen readers are software that are designed to turn text into speech. Blind people listen to the web. </p>

